{
  "id": "RAW_f3eb434d",
  "title": "资源不到万亿 OpenAI 的 1% ，Kimi 新模型超越 GPT-5",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg5NTc0MjgwMw==&mid=2247520753&idx=1&sn=a85edee562b36711b757bb2934bf0f7b",
  "date": "2025-11-07 11:58:00",
  "author": "Founder Park",
  "siteName": "Founder Park",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"background-color:inherit;font-family:sans-serif;\">时隔 4 个月，Kimi 推出了旗下开源模型 K2 的推理版本——K2 Thinking 模型，Kimi 迄今为止最强的开源思考模型。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 8px;visibility: visible;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <div data-pm-slice=\"3 3 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1T 参数，MoE 架构，32B 激活，原生 INT4 量化，256k 上下文，更好支持国产 GPU。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">官方评测成绩显示，K2 Thinking 在「人类最后的考试」的评测中，多项基准测试的表现达到了 SOTA 水平，不仅仅是开源领域，K2 Thinking 的测试成绩超过了同类型闭源模型。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100037086\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2046979865771812\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1192\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bb3dfcb8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FqpAK9iaV2O3sWk2s27M3ibXSXF921KAUw14kDjwFvq60a4bVfmianicuydQWAXn6zJYkdhnpDAZq7ZL6egQ1PX8mBQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">相比较 K2 模型，K2 Thinking 模型无需人工干预，可以自主实现高达 300 轮的工具调用和多轮思考能力，可以解决更复杂的问题。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">回过头来看，从 K2 到 K2 Thinking，从「模型即 Agent」到「模型即 Thinking Agent」，Kimi 正依靠自己的独特技术思考和判断，在资源受限的情况下，走上追赶乃至超过欧美 AI 巨头的道路。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不管怎么看，都有点热血漫的即视感。</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <div>\n      <hr style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;transform:scale(1, 0.5);text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-width:1px 0px 0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;transform-origin:0px 0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n      <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 36px;\"><span leaf=\"\">01&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></h2>\n      <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:16px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;color:rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:20px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;heading-2 ace-line old-record-id-Ptsvde2OHogt8cxXimscdqxJntd&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">K2 Thinking，</span></span></strong></h2>\n      <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;color:rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:20px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;heading-2 ace-line old-record-id-Ptsvde2OHogt8cxXimscdqxJntd&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">人类最后考试的 SOTA 模型</span></span></strong></h2>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">正如姚顺雨在《AI 下半场》中所说，「人工智能的下半场——从现在开始——将把重点从解决问题转移到定义问题。在这个新时代，评估将比训练更重要。」</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">模型能力持续进步的当下，评估变得比以往更加重要。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在 NMLU、GPQA 等传统基准测试已经无法有效体现模型能力的时候，人类最后的考试（Humanity's Last Exam，简称 HLE）在 2025 年应运而生。这是一个旨在评估当下最厉害的大模型的能力的基准测试集。由 Center for AI Safety 和 Scale AI 联合创建，测试内容几经调整，最终在 2025 年 3 月 4 日确定为一套包含了 2500 个前沿学术难题的题库，这些题分布在 100 多个不同的学科领域</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">，</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">由 50 多个国家的近 1000 名学科专家贡献。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在允许使用工具——搜索、Python、网络浏览工具的同等情况下，针对 Text-Only 的数据集的测试结果中，Kimi K2 Thinking 在这项基准评测中取得了 44.9% 的 SOTA 成绩。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100037090\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=da50eae1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FqpAK9iaV2O3sWk2s27M3ibXSXF921KAUw1MxnTnUk1MDDvwic3jPQzVo4pmFbcEcuIbusCuRptfJTBwv1LaQ5SXhA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">HLE 测试集最初发布时，旗舰模型的评测结果都不到 20%，到了今天大家基本都达到了超过 40% 的成绩，在数据的 Scaling Law 效果逐渐减小的当下，模型的能力确实还在一直进步中。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">甚至有了开源模型超过闭源模型的一幕。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除去官方的演示测试外，我们也看到了「歸藏的 AI 工具箱」、「赛博禅心」等自媒体作者的评测，不只是代码能力增强了，更明显的是，解决问题的综合能力真的提升了。</span></span></p>\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n         <p data-pm-slice=\"4 5 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"></p>\n         <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 36px;\"><span leaf=\"\">02&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></h2>\n         <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;color:rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:20px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;heading-2 ace-line old-record-id-Ptsvde2OHogt8cxXimscdqxJntd&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">当缸中之脑真正有了脚手架</span></span></strong></h2>\n         <p></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">回到 4 个月前，在 K2 初发布时，很多人的第一疑惑是——居然不是个推理模型？</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在 DeepSeek R1 已经成为全球级的现象事件时，一款非推理模型的开源，能带来多大的反响呢？</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Kimi 当时对外的回答是聚焦 Agent，做能更好调用工具的 Agent 模型。在我们与Kimi一位研究员的聊天中得知，其实在 K2 发布前，他们已经做过一个初版的 thinking 模型，但在 K2上线时，只先发布了 Agent 的前半截。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">8 月份张小珺对杨植麟的采访中，杨植麟在他认为的两种模型范式中，选择了后者。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">「一种是长思考的推理模型（Reasoning Model），以 o1 作为第一个做出来的代表。本质上，它通过让模型在过程中做很多尝试和反思，反思是其中重点。但它还是一个『缸中之脑』（brain in a vat），并不需要跟外界交互。」</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">「但有另一个很重要的范式，就是基于多轮的 Agent（智能体）强化学习范式，或者通过强化学习技术训练出来的 Agentic 模型，它的特点是会跟外界做很多交互。」</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">「但这两个东西都指向了同一个东西，是：test-time scaling（测试时扩展）。意思是，可以在测试时，或者在推理时，做到更好的规模化。」</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Kimi 当时选择了第二种方式，先做「交互」，然后再做「反思」，也就是今天的 K2 Thinking。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个有了脚手架的「缸中之脑」，用杨植麟的话说，「</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它可能是一个从『缸中之脑』变成可以跟世界交互，因为所谓 Agent 最重要的特征，就是它可以多轮地使用工具。</span></span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有两个关键点：一个是多轮，一个是工具。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">多轮就是你能做很多次，是 test time scaling（测试时扩展）的一种方式；工具则是连接这个『脑』跟外部世界的方式。」</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100037089\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.428955078125\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"4096\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5293e3db&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FqpAK9iaV2O3sWk2s27M3ibXSXF921KAUw1y2ohFyEl3WibZa5BQJKcz5cZGUgUiadQHszTVzWKnvSGKibtGgzRv0uTQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 5px 0px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">K2 Thinking 调用工具的能力有进一步提升</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当「缸中之脑」有了脚手架，模型的能力有了质的提升。所以才有了自主实现 300 轮工具调用和多轮思考的能力，实现了更强的 Agent 和推理性能。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">到了这一步，OpenAI 此前所设置的 AI 从 L1-L5 的分级，L3（Agent 智能体）可能才真的看到了曙光。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有趣的是，在 K2 Thinking 的 API 调用说明中可以看到，模型的多步工具调用，需要把上下文中所有的思考内容（reasoning_content 字段）返回给模型进行多次推理，保持推理的连贯性。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">类似这样的能力，是 Claude 的「extended thinking」（扩展思考），同样也是支持把推理结果持续带入后续步骤。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在当下，这是一种非共识的技术思路，OpenAI 的 GPT 系列和 Google 的 Gemini 模型都没有支持这个功能。</span></span></p>\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n         <p data-pm-slice=\"4 5 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"></p>\n         <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 36px;\"><span leaf=\"\">03&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></h2>\n         <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;color:rgb(75, 110, 245);font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:20px;font-family:PingFangSC-Light;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;heading-2 ace-line old-record-id-Ptsvde2OHogt8cxXimscdqxJntd&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">资源悬殊下的逆风局</span></span></strong></h2>\n         <p></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在 K2 Thinking 模型发布后，我们在 X（推特）上看到了一张有趣的图。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100037088\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1472995090016367\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1222\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5784d74b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FqpAK9iaV2O3sWk2s27M3ibXSXF921KAUw1aUqC8k0l0ia5LN37F62ahDDZhQqrugqevnUubPrMABDJYRtRGLrRkgg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">按照这位博主的说法，在 HLE 上达到了全球 SOTA 能力的 K2 Thinking，所属公司月之暗面目前的估值是 OpenAI 的 0.5%，是 Anthropic 和 Grok 的 2%。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">或者我们可以用更详细的一个数据来进一步对比。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Kimi 去年的估值是 33 亿美元，即便算上最近传言中的新融资，推算新估值仍在几十亿美元级别。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而马斯克的 Grok（xAI），截至 2025 年 9 月底，估值约为 2000 亿美元。可以顺便看看另外两家的估值情况，在完成今年 9 月份 F 轮 130 亿美元的融资后，Anthropic 目前的估值是 1830 亿美元；OpenAI 最新的估值是 5000 亿美元，成为全球最具价值的私营公司之一。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">与此同时，xAI 拥有目前全球规模最大的 GPU 集群之一——20 万块 H100 GPU 的 Colossus 超级计算机集群，员工总数超过 1200 人，据估计 Grok 4 的训练成本可能达到了 4900 万美元。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而 Kimi，公司人数 200 人左右，据外媒报道，训练成本约 460 万美元。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对中国的基模公司来说，都面临「缺显卡」、资源相对稀缺的现状，融资太少、卡太贵。与 OpenAI、Google 等美国巨头相比，试错机会少、成本压力大。要想活下来，必须精确地把每一步的执行都做对。K2 Thinking在多轮思考和调用工具的能力上超过GTP5、Grok4等国外闭源模型，让中国 AI 创业公司用不到 1% 的资源，完成了对万亿巨头的逆风翻盘。</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:5px 0px 24px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">未来，是否会像黄仁勋对《金融时报》所说的那样，「中国将在人工智能竞赛中击败美国」，局势正在改变。</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Kimi 新模型 K2 Thinking 凭借 MoE 架构和 Agentic 能力，在资源远低于巨头的情况下，于权威基准测试中超越 GPT-5 等闭源模型，展现中国 AI 创新实力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Kimi 新模型 K2 Thinking 凭借 MoE 架构和 Agentic 能力，在资源远低于巨头的情况下，于权威基准测试中超越 GPT-5 等闭源模型，展现中国 AI 创新实力。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了 Kimi 团队推出的开源推理模型 K2 Thinking，该模型具备 1T 参数、MoE 架构、原生 INT4 量化和 256k 上下文，并支持国产 GPU。官方评测显示，K2 Thinking 在“人类最后的考试”（Humanity's Last Exam， HLE）中取得了 44.9%的 SOTA（State-of-the-Art）成绩，不仅在开源领域领先，甚至超越了同类型闭源模型。文章强调 K2 Thinking 从“模型即 Agent”发展到“模型即 Thinking Agent”，能够自主实现高达 300 轮的工具调用和多轮思考，解决了更复杂的问题。文章还对比了月之暗面（Kimi 母公司）与 OpenAI、xAI 等国际巨头在资源上的巨大悬殊，指出 Kimi 以不到 1%的资源实现了技术上的“逆风翻盘”，展现了中国 AI 在资源受限下的高效创新能力，并展望了中国 AI 在全球竞争中的潜力。",
